321
00:27:04,150 --> 00:27:05,740
Tidak begitu berlebihan
seperti ucapanmu.

322
00:27:05,950 --> 00:27:07,940
Jenderal, kau masih seperti dulu.

323
00:27:08,340 --> 00:27:10,100
Kakak Seperguruan, kau kurusan.

324
00:27:14,740 --> 00:27:15,670
Bagaimana kondisi militer?

325
00:27:15,670 --> 00:27:17,060
Jenderal, jangan khawatir.
Semuanya baik-baik saja.

326
00:27:17,340 --> 00:27:18,740
Tiga hari kemudian,
kita akan tiba di Kota Nan.

327
00:27:19,150 --> 00:27:21,740
